    "edgeCases": 7,
    "wcagLevel": "AA"
  },
  "tokens": { "total": 26, "prefix": "cal", "mode": "C" },
  "componentDescriptions": {
    "DayCell": "Celda individual de día. 10 States (incluye range-start/end/middle, today, other-month). Sizes: sm/md.\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• role='gridcell' + aria-label con fecha completa\n• aria-selected en selected\n• aria-current='date' en today\n• aria-disabled en disabled\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• Arrow keys navegan\n• Enter/Space selecciona\n\n🎯 Focus:\n• Roving tabindex\n• Range middle: sin radius para efecto 'pill' continuo\n\nWCAG 2.2 AA.",
    "Calendar": "Grid de fechas standalone. Mode: single/range. Scale: compact (sidebar widget) / comfortable (popover default) / fullscreen (dashboard page — Ant pattern). VisibleMonths: 1 o 2 (range selection con 2).\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• role='grid' + aria-label dinámico (mes año)\n• Heading mes/año en aria-live='polite'\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• Arrow keys día a día\n• Page Up/Down cambia mes\n• Home/End inicio/fin semana\n\n🎯 Focus:\n• Roving tabindex\n• RTL: arrow keys auto-flip\n\nTokens: 26, prefijo cal-.\nWCAG 2.2 AA.\n\nScope: standalone calendar widget. Para form input con popover usa DatePicker. Para range con 2 inputs + presets usa DateRangePicker."
  },
  "variableBindings": {
    "cal/sm/cell": "sizing/32",
    "cal/md/cell": "sizing/40",
    "cal/cell/radius": "radius/pill",
    "cal/default/bg": "surface/default",
